{
  "texts": [
    "The effect of treatments is approximated by computing the distance between the morphological features of treatments and controls.",
    "We use batch-corrected features obtained with CellProfiler (with sphering regularization parameter 1e-2) in the following way:",
    "Calculate the median profile of control wells within the same plate (median control profile of the plate). 2.",
    "For each treated well, calculate the Euclidean distance between its well-level profile and the median control profile of its plate. 3.",
    "Estimate the distribution of control well distances against the median control profile per plate."
  ]
}